{"tid":1657938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拳王阿里前妻：LBJ無法跟阿里一樣偉大","createTime":"2019-10-16T10:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T21:11:44.000Z","uid":33359,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"28808afe8d644f395394b7ad39fb3eebbda79a00","tid":1657938,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"昨天 LBJ 助紂為虐，抨擊自家人莫里，被美國鄉民出征到爆<br />\n<br />\n今天美國人權主義者，同時也是世界拳王的阿里前妻在受訪中表示<br />\n<br />\nLBJ不是阿里LeBron James is not a Muhammad Ali<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/yxww7ec4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fyxww7ec4&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=22972de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/yxww7ec4</a><br />\n<br />\n全文大意為，LBJ 針對 Morey 力挺香港的言論，提出批評，這件事情註定讓他的歷史定<br />\n位，無法如同拳王阿里一樣，是個偉大的人權捍衛者。阿里的前妻認為 LBJ 是有可能成<br />\n為如同阿里一樣偉大的運動員，他其實並不需要選邊站，他現在的身份地位，應該有足夠<br />\n的影響力改變世界。如果她是 LBJ 她會選擇替「香港」發聲，因為香港是為人權與自由<br />\n在奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n不過有些人可能覺得莫名其妙，阿里前妻沒事出來刷什麼存在感，其實事情是這樣的，<br />\n2016 年 6 月拳王阿里離世，那時候 LBJ 曾說過「沒有阿里，就沒有現在的自己」，感<br />\n念阿里在 70 年代為了黑人平權的努力。<br />\n<br />\n而文中也有提到，2017年時她稱 LBJ 為「the Muhammad Ali of basketball」，籃球界<br />\n的阿里，讚譽 LBJ 在美國社會上的成就。<br />\n<br />\n而 LBJ 也曾經用「More than an athlete」，宣示自己並非單純只是個運動員，捍衛自<br />\n己對於美國社會議題的發言權，其實就是在嗆川普。<br />\n<br />\n結果 LBJ 卻選擇忽視人權毀滅者對香港的惡行惡狀，以及明明是中國玻璃心才全面抵制<br />\nNBA 的腦羞，為了那幾場被取消的熱身賽周邊活動，砲口向內打擊自己人的言論自由權，<br />\n向中國市場及人民幣低頭，被靠北也是剛好而已，不否認聯盟天下第一人的「強大」，但<br />\n這個聯盟天下第一人再也配不上「偉大」兩字。<br />\n<br />\n附上原文跟 NBA 板友 dragon803 大大的分段翻譯<br />\n<br />\nMuhammad Ali&rsquo;s second wife KO&rsquo;d LeBron James on Tuesday over his<br />\ncontroversial remarks regarding the pro-democracy protests in Hong Kong,<br />\nsaying he&rsquo;s not a &ldquo;man of the world&rdquo; like the late boxing legend.<br />\n<br />\n阿里的第二任妻子對於LBJ星期二對香港發表的聲明說他並不像已經過世的拳擊傳奇一樣<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;LeBron is not a Muhammad Ali, no,&rdquo; Khalilah Ali told TMZ Sports.<br />\n<br />\nLBJ不是阿里，絕對不是<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;But he could be. He could be. He could be a man of the world instead of<br />\njust taking sides against other people. But when it comes to the world, he&rsquo;s<br />\nnot a Muhammad Ali because he made that statement. That makes him different<br />\nthan Muhammad Ali.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n但他可以成為，他原本是可以成為的，他可以成為改變世界的男人的而不僅僅是選邊站，<br />\n他並不是阿里因為他發表了那個聲明，這使他跟阿里有所不同<br />\n<br />\nKhalilah, who in 2017 likened James to &ldquo;the Muhammad Ali of basketball&rdquo; for<br />\nspeaking out about racism in America, said she still loved the Lakers<br />\nsuperstar and called him &ldquo;the greatest,&rdquo; which was Muhammad&rsquo;s<br />\nself-anointed nickname.<br />\n<br />\nKnaliah曾經在2017年稱呼LBJ是籃球界的阿里，因為他在美國談論種族議題，說她還是喜愛著這位湖人超級球星並且稱呼the greatness(阿里的綽號)<br />\n<br />\nBut she insisted that &ldquo;you have to stay [the] course when it comes to human,<br />\nrespect, human rights, human liberty.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n但她堅持在事情攸關人民，尊重以及人權跟人權自由時，你必須要堅持到底<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;In Lebron&rsquo;s shoes, I would stand up for the people in Hong Kong,&rdquo; she<br />\nsaid.<br />\n<br />\n如果站在LBJ的處境，我會選擇替香港發聲<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;You cannot stand aside and not, you know, be a part of somebody who&rsquo;s<br />\nfighting for their rights, fighting for their freedom.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n當人們面對自由與人權而戰時，你不該忽視它<br />\n<br />\nKhalilah, who was married to Muhammad from 1967 to 1977, also referenced the<br />\nprotesters who burned replicas of James&rsquo; jersey in Hong Kong earlier in the<br />\nday.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;They would not take Muhammad Ali&rsquo;s shorts and burn them anywhere. It would<br />\nnot happen,&rdquo; she said.<br />\n<br />\n至少阿里的衣服不會被任意的燒毀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1571215054.A.F61.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1571215054.A.F61.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=33bf752e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1571215054.A.F61.html</a>"},{"pid":"883ede5468b1878a0625359cbe4aed9f3e28109a","tid":1657938,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cb058df86b6d3a755c6224fc3f8c309f256f9f4c","tid":1657938,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"是<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92a19df675177923fbf9414506965ebe5f85b2b","tid":1657938,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"睇條撚樣平時都得罪人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇fd幫手講好說話嘅"},{"pid":"41646fa5fb185849cf0a70451a5d6830e3eeed38","tid":1657938,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e58aa5192cb8cb7fe59ff20677de0dd3ea37073","tid":1657938,"uid":154486,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打燒衫！！<br />\n燒衫好野！多謝燒衫！"},{"pid":"ed67401fd2d64a08867e8d71ff9565a03b7bf65d","tid":1657938,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"淨係瘋狂轉會為冠軍就知佢唔配,依家仲衰多兩錢重,去支那呃傻仔啦"},{"pid":"93ace770734b076f32dfc1de79a09d2bc69f4507","tid":1657938,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"似少少馬丁D孫出來屌可以話以後唔洗美國打波"},{"pid":"cc47d53534761016babf407c2e1834ebdee57b05","tid":1657938,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass